WEBVTT

1
00:50:19.800 --> 00:50:22.600 
属实 但那些血流得有意义
True, but always with purpose.

2
00:50:22.600 --> 00:50:24.600 
都是为了达成伟大的目标
Always with greater goals.

3
00:50:24.600 --> 00:50:27.400 
而这纯属不必要的牺牲
This was simply an unnecessary casualty.

4
00:50:27.600 --> 00:50:31.400 
作为自我惩罚 我选择不再与你交战
As penance, I chose not to make war with you again...

5
00:50:31.400 --> 00:50:34.800 
并试图挽回我导致的伤害
...and to attempt to rectify this disservice.

6
00:50:34.800 --> 00:50:36.100 
挽回
Rectify?

7
00:50:36.400 --> 00:50:37.700 
是的
Yes.

8
00:50:37.800 --> 00:50:40.800 
我希望能将你失去的归还与你
I had hoped to return to you what you had lost.

9
00:50:43.550 --> 00:50:46.900 
我已在这世上行走近六个世纪
I have walked this world for nearly six centuries.

10
00:50:47.200 --> 00:50:48.550 
如你所知
As you know...

11
00:50:48.600 --> 00:50:53.400 
靠的是浸泡拉撒路坑中的回春之水
...I achieve this by bathing in the rejuvenating waters of the Lazarus Pit.

